title: LeagueClient.exe - Entry Point Not Found
body: **"The procedure entry point CT_POLICY_EVAL_CTX_set_time could not be located in the dynamic link library libcrypto-1_1.dll."** appears every time i click launch on the league leagacy client and also when i try to launch the alpha client. Anyone know what i can do to fix this, as i cant play league at all.

replies.body:
Hey there,

Could you try reinstalling league of legends, please run the installer as Administrator (Right click > Run as Administrator) when attempting to install the game.
